title: Suicide Boat Rams Saudi Arabian Warship
text:
Browse Channels Suicide Boat Rams Saudi Arabian Warship 
Video has emerged of the moment a suicide boat rammed a Saudi frigate last week — an attack believed to have been intended for a US warship. The video was filmed from the frigate’s air operations observation platform overlooking the helicopter pad on the rear of the ship. It had been previously reported by local media in the area that the ship had been hit by a guided missile. But the footage reveals a Yemeni rebel speed boat dashing over the horizon and into the warship’s stern.
